{% set workflows = workflows | default([]) %}{% set agents = agents | default([]) %}{% set skills = skills | default([]) %}{% set rules = rules | default([]) %}{% set patterns = patterns | default([]) %}{% set blueprints = blueprints | default([]) %}{% set templates = templates | default([]) %}{% set tests = tests | default([]) %}{% set knowledge = knowledge | default([]) %}{% set scripts = scripts | default([]) %}{% set memory_queries = memory_queries | default([]) %}<div style="font-family:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;line-height:1.4;color:#1a1a1a;max-width:900px;">{% if requirements %}<section style="margin-bottom:8px;"><h3 style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb;padding-bottom:2px;margin:0 0 4px 0;color:#111827;font-size:1em;"><span>📋</span> Requirements</h3>{% if requirements is string %}<div style="color:#374151;">{{ requirements | trim }}</div>{% else %}<ul style="margin:0;padding-left:18px;color:#374151;">{% for r in requirements %}<li style="margin-bottom:2px;">{{ r | trim }}</li>{% endfor %}</ul>{% endif %}</section>{% endif %}{% if acceptance_criteria %}<section style="margin-bottom:8px;"><h3 style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb;padding-bottom:2px;margin:0 0 4px 0;color:#111827;font-size:1em;"><span>✅</span> Acceptance Criteria</h3>{% if acceptance_criteria is string %}<div style="color:#374151;">{{ acceptance_criteria | trim }}</div>{% else %}<ul style="margin:0;padding-left:18px;color:#374151;">{% for c in acceptance_criteria %}<li style="margin-bottom:2px;">{{ c | trim }}</li>{% endfor %}</ul>{% endif %}</section>{% endif %}<section style="margin-bottom:8px;padding:8px;background-color:#f9fafb;border-radius:4px;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;"><h3 style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;margin:0 0 6px 0;color:#111827;font-size:0.95em;"><span>🏭</span> Factory Assets</h3><div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;">{% if workflows %}<div><span style="color:#4b5563;font-size:0.8em;font-weight:600;margin-right:2px;">🔄 Workflows:</span>{% for w in workflows %}<code style="background:#eef2ff;color:#4338ca;padding:0 3px;border-radius:2px;font-size:0.75em;">{{ w }}</code>{% if not loop.last %} {% endif %}{% endfor %}</div>{% endif %}{% if agents %}<div><span style="color:#4b5563;font-size:0.8em;font-weight:600;margin-right:2px;">👤 Agents:</span>{% for a in agents %}<code style="background:#fdf2f8;color:#be185d;padding:0 3px;border-radius:2px;font-size:0.75em;">{{ a }}</code>{% if not loop.last %} {% endif %}{% endfor %}</div>{% endif %}{% if skills %}<div><span style="color:#4b5563;font-size:0.8em;font-weight:600;margin-right:2px;">🧩 Skills:</span>{% for s in skills %}<code style="background:#f0fdf4;color:#15803d;padding:0 3px;border-radius:2px;font-size:0.75em;">{{ s }}</code>{% if not loop.last %} {% endif %}{% endfor %}</div>{% endif %}</div>{% if rules or patterns or blueprints or templates %}<div style="margin-top:6px;padding-top:6px;border-top:1px dashed #d1d5db;display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;">{% if rules %}<div><span style="color:#4b5563;font-size:0.8em;font-weight:600;margin-right:2px;">📏 Rules:</span>{% for r in rules %}<code style="background:#fff7ed;color:#c2410c;padding:0 3px;border-radius:2px;font-size:0.75em;">{{ r }}</code>{% if not loop.last %} {% endif %}{% endfor %}</div>{% endif %}{% if patterns %}<div><span style="color:#4b5563;font-size:0.8em;font-weight:600;margin-right:2px;">📐 Patterns:</span>{% for p in patterns %}<code style="background:#f5f3ff;color:#6d28d9;padding:0 3px;border-radius:2px;font-size:0.75em;">{{ p }}</code>{% if not loop.last %} {% endif %}{% endfor %}</div>{% endif %}{% if blueprints %}<div><span style="color:#4b5563;font-size:0.8em;font-weight:600;margin-right:2px;">🎨 Blueprints:</span>{% for b in blueprints %}<code style="background:#ecfeff;color:#0e7490;padding:0 3px;border-radius:2px;font-size:0.75em;">{{ b }}</code>{% if not loop.last %} {% endif %}{% endfor %}</div>{% endif %}{% if templates %}<div><span style="color:#4b5563;font-size:0.8em;font-weight:600;margin-right:2px;">📋 Templates:</span>{% for t in templates %}<code style="background:#f8fafc;color:#475569;padding:0 3px;border-radius:2px;font-size:0.75em;">{{ t }}</code>{% if not loop.last %} {% endif %}{% endfor %}</div>{% endif %}</div>{% endif %}</section><section style="margin-bottom:8px;"><h3 style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb;padding-bottom:2px;margin:0 0 4px 0;color:#111827;font-size:1em;"><span>🧪</span> Test Strategy</h3><ul style="margin:0;padding-left:18px;color:#374151;">{% if tests %}{% for t in tests %}<li style="margin-bottom:2px;"><strong style="color:#0366d6;">[{{ t.type | upper }}]</strong> {% if t.script %}<code style="color:#24292e;font-size:0.85em;">{{ t.script }}</code>: {% endif %}<span style="color:#586069;font-size:0.9em;">{{ t.expected | trim }}</span></li>{% endfor %}{% else %}<li style="color:#9ca3af;font-size:0.9em;"><em>No tests.</em></li>{% endif %}</ul></section>{% if scripts or knowledge or memory_queries %}<section style="margin-bottom:8px;padding:6px;border:1px solid #d1d5db;border-radius:4px;font-size:0.85em;"><h4 style="margin:0 0 4px 0;color:#24292e;">📚 Context</h4><div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;color:#444;">{% if scripts %}<div><strong>Scripts:</strong> {% for s in scripts %}<code>{{ s }}</code>{% if not loop.last %}, {% endif %}{% endfor %}</div>{% endif %}{% if knowledge %}<div><strong>Knowledge:</strong> {% for k in knowledge %}<code>{{ k.name }}</code>{% if not loop.last %}, {% endif %}{% endfor %}</div>{% endif %}{% if memory_queries %}<div><strong>Memory:</strong> {% for mq in memory_queries %}<code>{{ mq }}</code>{% if not loop.last %}, {% endif %}{% endfor %}</div>{% endif %}</div></section>{% endif %}{% if schema_json %}<details style="margin-top:8px;border:1px solid #d1d5db;border-radius:4px;background-color:#f6f8fa;"><summary style="padding:4px 8px;cursor:pointer;font-weight:600;color:#24292e;font-size:0.85em;">🛠️ Schema (Expand)</summary><div style="padding:6px;border-top:1px solid #d1d5db;"><pre style="margin:0;font-size:0.75em;overflow-x:auto;"><code>{{ schema_json }}</code></pre></div></details>{% endif %}{% if notes %}<div style="margin-top:8px;border-left:3px solid #0366d6;padding:4px 10px;background-color:#f1f8ff;color:#0366d6;font-size:0.9em;"><strong style="display:block;margin-bottom:1px;">📝 Notes</strong>{{ notes | trim }}</div>{% endif %}</div>
